sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Jupyter as Jupyter Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: User Accesses Jupyter Workbench

    User->>Router: GET /notebook/{namespace}/{username}/lab<br/>HTTPS Request
    Router->>OAuth: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS with internal CA<br/>Port 8443/TCP
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift OAuth Token
    OAuth->>Jupyter: Forward to JupyterLab<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>Localhost (no encryption)
    Jupyter->>Jupyter: Render JupyterLab UI
    Jupyter-->>OAuth: HTML Response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JupyterLab Interface

    Note over User,S3: User Opens Notebook and Loads Data

    User->>Router: Execute Python Code in Notebook
    Router->>OAuth: Forward Request
    OAuth->>Jupyter: Execute Code
    Jupyter->>S3: Read Data from S3<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>S3 Credentials (AWS SigV4)
    S3-->>Jupyter: Return Data
    Jupyter-->>OAuth: Results
    OAuth-->>Router: Results
    Router-->>User: Display Results in Notebook

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Kubeflow Pipeline Task Execution

    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipeline Controller
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container (Pod)
    participant KFP_API as Kubeflow API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    KFP->>Runtime: Launch Pipeline Task Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Runtime->>S3: Download Input Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>AWS SigV4 Auth
    S3-->>Runtime: Artifacts
    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute Python Task
    Runtime->>S3: Upload Output Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>AWS SigV4 Auth
    Runtime->>KFP_API: Report Task Status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    KFP_API-->>Runtime: Acknowledgment
    Runtime->>KFP: Task Complete

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Image Build and Deployment

    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant UBI as UBI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Quay as Quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ImageStream as OpenShift ImageStream

    Konflux->>GitHub: Clone Source Code<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Git Token
    GitHub-->>Konflux: Source Code
    Konflux->>UBI: Pull Base Image<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Pull Secret
    UBI-->>Konflux: UBI9 Python Base
    Konflux->>Konflux: Build Multi-Arch Image<br/>linux/x86_64, arm64, ppc64le, s390x
    Konflux->>Quay: Push Image<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Push Secret
    ImageStream->>Quay: Pull Image Reference<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Pull Secret
    Quay-->>ImageStream: Image Available
